snippet.title: Re:Zombie Girl Side S - Sister - PT 1 (R:ZGS)
snippet.description:
Welcome to Re:Zombie Girl Side S -Sister-

No Audio it has been a while guys sorry.

I'm not comfortable to speak yet...

Mobile Game

Rated T: Fantasy Violence

4.4* Rating in Google Play store

Google Play Link: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.karapon.zsren

Will two sisters find a bright future, or despair?

Feed zombies to give back the intelligence they have lost, and solve the mystery that haunts both sisters.

The story has multiple endings depending on the actions you choose for the futures of both sisters.

Game By: Karapon.Games
